I am so honored to be the new Youth Worship team leader for the First Baptist Church of Glenarden. Even with all the amazing opportunities that being an opera singer has afforded me, I have felt the Lord calling me to other things in this next season of my life. I will still do classical and operatic performances. This is not a departure, it’s just a pivot! Do what you love & take care of yourself. <3
